-- Turkish March Tourist Arrivals Rise Annual 17.1 Percent to 1.4 Million
-- Ali Berat Meric
-- 2010-04-26T08:01:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/turkish-march-tourist-arrivals-rise-annual-17-1-percent-to-1-4-million.html

          
          
             The number of foreign tourists
visiting Turkey rose 17.1 percent in March from a year
earlier.  
 About 1.4 million foreign visitors arrived in the month, up
from 1.2 million in the same month of 2009, the Tourism Ministry
in Ankara said on its Web site today.  
 Tourists increased 11.2 percent in the first quarter from a
year ago, the ministry said.  
